{
  "AWSTemplateFormatVersion": "2010-09-09",

  "Description": "AWS CloudFormation Sample Template Create an Amazon EC2 instance running the DShop AMI. This example creates an EC2 security group for the instance to give you SSH access. **WARNING** This template creates an Amazon EC2 instance. You will be billed for the AWS resources used if you create a stack from this template.",

